{"tid":878193,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"為什麼兔仔鼻子會移動?","createTime":"2018-10-27T02:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T04:35:42.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"441c716bd49e8c7805f7130ce790bd7d0b8b8030","tid":878193,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"兔子的鼻子移動時代表當時專注，可以因為牠對某事物感興趣或好奇，移動得越快就越專注。但鼻子移動亦可以代表焦慮，要看當時的情況。通常兔子感到輕鬆時牠們鼻子會移動。<br />\n<br />\n你可以做一個有趣的實驗(或可變成一個對話技巧)：趴在地上面向着兔子，重複地把上唇卷入上牙下面來模仿兔子鼻子移動(如果有鬍子會更有效)，然後改變速度看看兔子的反應。移動速度首先比兔兔慢，然後加速，牠可能會因為專注程度增加而跟你加速，然後你再減慢，此時牠亦可能跟著減慢。牠亦可能會覺得迷惑。(最好做之前告訴家人以免覺得怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到兔子鼻子移動：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Tozjowr2JY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8Tozjowr2JY&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2umi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ef7bd5ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Tozjowr2JY</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊來源: </span><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/follow-my-nose/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Ffollow-my-nose%2F&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2umi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=bcc4b801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/follow-my-nose/</a>"},{"pid":"6a4bda6b846f17fe9080efb6194d6c6e74bd3a70","tid":878193,"uid":16161,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n你可以做一個有趣的實驗(或可變成一個對話技巧)：趴在地上面向着兔子，重複地把上唇卷入上牙下面來模仿兔子鼻子移動</span><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後真係走左去跟住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後發覺好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a7d63085a52d18fadfa7